Package: database
Title: WRB hydro database creation and maintenance
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Ghislain", "de Laplante", , "ghislaindel@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-5093-9185"))
Description: Set of functions for the initial creation and ongling maintenance of WRB's local database. This local database is a combination of the Water Survey of Canada real-time and historical data and WRB data held in Aquarius; in addition, multiple parameters are calculated to facilitate reporting and graphically representing data.
